@host = http://localhost:48080

### UCA-Base 系统状态页面
GET {{host}}/

### UCA-Base 自身健康状态
GET {{host}}/actuator/health

### 注册 Auth 实例 1
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/applications/auth/instances/auth-1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicationName": "认证模块",
  "baseUrl": "http://auth-1:8080",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "metadata": {
    "zone": "default"
  }
}

### 注册 Auth 实例 2
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/applications/auth/instances/auth-2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicationName": "认证模块",
  "baseUrl": "http://auth-2:8080",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "metadata": {
    "zone": "default"
  }
}

### Auth 实例 1 心跳
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/applications/auth/instances/auth-1/heartbeat

### 轮询发现，连续执行会在在线实例之间切换
GET {{host}}/api/v1/applications/auth/instances/next

### 查询全部应用状态
GET {{host}}/api/v1/applications

### 查询 Auth 状态
GET {{host}}/api/v1/applications/auth

### 主动注销 Auth 实例 1
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/applications/auth/instances/auth-1
